            </h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-blue-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-all group">
                    <div class="flex items-start mb-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mr-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                            <i class="fas fa-handshake text-white text-xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-gray-900 mb-2">Contract Disputes</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
